::EndBringer/Killfest/Incarcinator/Scyther::

EndBringer continues to send electricity through Double Punch, and 
makes his way away from most of the fighting.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killfest manuevers out of the way of a missile and then fires one 
back at Vehement. He recieves Darkfate's message and replies. "I'm 
here. What do you need?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator looks down at Menasor, looking to see whether or not his 
shots had hit.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Seeing Iron Raptor taking his target, Scyther quickly picks out 
another one. He takes out his scythe and flies up silently behind 
Megatron, still cloaked, swiping it quickly at the Decepticon's head.
